WEBVTT

01:26.640 --> 01:35.009
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.470 --> 01:37.920
[Episode 1]

01:38.810 --> 01:41.600
[1994, Yantai, Shandong]

01:44.620 --> 01:45.350
Come on, come on!

01:45.350 --> 01:45.780
Here.

01:47.420 --> 01:47.950
Weigh it!

01:48.900 --> 01:50.500
Load this crate onto Truck One.

01:50.500 --> 01:51.100
Truck One.

01:53.570 --> 01:54.620
A bad one.

02:00.840 --> 02:01.370
Weigh it!

02:14.650 --> 02:15.180
Shengli,

02:15.620 --> 02:17.300
any news on that script of yours?

02:17.300 --> 02:18.700
I'll hear back very soon!

02:21.430 --> 02:23.630
If you want something different...

02:26.340 --> 02:27.480
If you want something different...

02:27.480 --> 02:31.670
[Jinhai Seafood Processing Plant]

02:41.780 --> 02:42.710
Unload the fish!

02:45.620 --> 02:46.150
Let's go.

02:47.560 --> 02:48.190
Feng!

02:48.910 --> 02:49.410
Feng!

02:50.650 --> 02:51.240
Shengli!

02:52.079 --> 02:52.910
Back from the supply run?

02:52.120 --> 02:54.410
[Porter's Lodge]

02:53.430 --> 02:54.520
L-Let's go for lunch.

02:54.520 --> 02:55.720
Any mail for me today?

02:55.880 --> 03:02.090
[Porter's Lodge]

02:58.020 --> 02:59.710
Well... early this morning,

03:00.470 --> 03:01.800
Director Wang took your letter

03:01.800 --> 03:02.430
again.

03:03.590 --> 03:05.320
He still hasn't given it to you?

03:07.530 --> 03:08.430
No, S-Shengli!

03:08.500 --> 03:09.900
Don't tell him I told you!

03:13.510 --> 03:17.350
[Certificate]

03:14.400 --> 03:16.090
Xu Shengli's handwriting

03:16.470 --> 03:17.870
is actually pretty good.

03:18.020 --> 03:18.400
Liu.

03:18.460 --> 03:20.190
What's the use?

03:20.190 --> 03:22.240
-Did he even write it himself?
-Drinking at noon?

03:22.240 --> 03:24.970
-What if someone sees it?
-There's no one around.

03:25.150 --> 03:25.910
You don't get flushed anyway.

03:25.910 --> 03:26.690
I know that.

03:26.810 --> 03:27.140
Here.

03:27.930 --> 03:28.930
Here, let me do it.

03:30.500 --> 03:31.190
It's okay. It's okay.

03:31.190 --> 03:31.560
I'll get it.

03:31.560 --> 03:32.220
I'll wipe it.

03:32.220 --> 03:33.150
Wipe it.

03:38.970 --> 03:40.030
Director, where is my letter?

03:40.030 --> 03:40.760
What letter?

03:41.360 --> 03:42.680
It's lunch break!

03:43.060 --> 03:44.520
Come back this afternoon!

03:50.130 --> 03:51.260
These aren't yours!

03:51.810 --> 03:52.710
What are you doing?

03:52.710 --> 03:53.510
Aren't you...

03:54.300 --> 03:54.960
Xu Shengli!

03:56.079 --> 03:56.650
Get off!

03:58.210 --> 03:59.800
What are you doing?

03:59.900 --> 04:00.620
Xu Shengli!

04:02.810 --> 04:03.590
What are you doing?

04:03.590 --> 04:06.280
Who gave you the right
to take my registered mail?

04:06.280 --> 04:07.660
Film studio?

04:08.280 --> 04:10.480
A film studio is still another company!

04:10.680 --> 04:12.150
A couple of lousy skits

04:12.150 --> 04:13.240
and some crappy awards

04:13.240 --> 04:14.530
don't make you somebody!

04:14.530 --> 04:15.240
Listen up,

04:16.160 --> 04:17.690
you're just an ordinary worker

04:17.690 --> 04:19.060
at the seafood processing plant!

04:19.060 --> 04:20.769
You're just like your mom—

04:21.010 --> 04:22.190
always overreaching!

04:22.190 --> 04:23.010
Back then, she had to
take the college entrance exam—

04:23.010 --> 04:24.220
but did she get in?

04:24.390 --> 04:25.630
She ended up back here
grilling fish anyway!

04:25.630 --> 04:26.690
It's her fate.

04:26.800 --> 04:27.860
It's your fate too!

04:27.930 --> 04:29.390
Your whole family's fate!

04:30.660 --> 04:31.990
What are you staring at?

04:32.360 --> 04:33.620
This is your stuff, isn't it?

04:33.620 --> 04:34.190
Take it!

04:35.159 --> 04:36.040
If you want to work, work!

04:36.040 --> 04:37.010
If not, get lost!

04:38.240 --> 04:40.740
[Outstanding
Environmental Compliance Enterprise]

04:47.690 --> 04:48.220
Get lost!

04:56.860 --> 04:57.930
What are you all looking at?

04:57.930 --> 04:58.860
Get back to work!

04:59.810 --> 05:00.670
Close the door.

05:03.130 --> 05:03.540
Liu.

05:03.810 --> 05:04.450
Director.

05:04.450 --> 05:05.050
It's okay.

05:05.680 --> 05:07.450
I'm here. What are you afraid of?

05:07.450 --> 05:08.740
I was so scared.

05:09.040 --> 05:10.330
My heart...

05:10.430 --> 05:11.680
-is still pounding hard.
-Did he hurt you?

05:11.680 --> 05:12.300
No.

05:12.510 --> 05:13.100
What about you?

05:13.100 --> 05:14.100
Are you all right?

05:14.100 --> 05:15.220
He would never dare do something to me.

05:15.220 --> 05:17.620
A brat like that
needs to be put in his place!

05:19.430 --> 05:20.300
Shengli, Shengli!

05:20.300 --> 05:22.560
Let's talk this out! Don't be impulsive!

05:26.910 --> 05:28.260
[Technical Department]
[Quality Inspection Department]

05:28.260 --> 05:31.460
[Finance Department]
[Personnel Department]

05:29.100 --> 05:29.800
Security!

05:29.800 --> 05:30.450
Help!

05:30.450 --> 05:31.070
Shengli!

05:32.070 --> 05:32.960
Put that down!

05:37.159 --> 05:38.159
Stop right there!

05:39.250 --> 05:40.560
Don't run! Stop!

05:41.830 --> 05:43.430
Stop right there! Don't run!

05:50.930 --> 05:51.620
Son,

05:52.060 --> 05:54.159
I got you some ice. Here.

05:56.540 --> 05:58.050
Put it on yourself first.

05:59.450 --> 06:01.040
Are you hurt anywhere else?

06:01.360 --> 06:02.760
Let's go to the hospital.

06:02.930 --> 06:04.370
No need. I'm really fine.

06:05.560 --> 06:06.350
It's okay.

06:06.950 --> 06:09.080
We've already paid the compensation.

06:09.180 --> 06:10.690
Later, I'll take you

06:10.690 --> 06:12.660
to see Director Wang
and the factory leaders—

06:12.660 --> 06:14.010
we'll apologize properly,

06:14.010 --> 06:15.930
and this whole thing will blow over.

06:15.930 --> 06:17.330
Mom, I did nothing wrong.

06:17.430 --> 06:18.570
Why should I apologize?

06:18.570 --> 06:20.770
I've long wanted to quit this lousy job!

06:21.330 --> 06:22.130
"Lousy job?"

06:22.750 --> 06:23.570
Your mom and I

06:23.570 --> 06:24.430
begged everyone we knew

06:24.430 --> 06:25.830
to get you this lousy job,

06:25.950 --> 06:26.920
letting you take over your mom's position

06:26.920 --> 06:27.650
at the plant!

06:28.630 --> 06:30.230
It's a state-owned factory.

06:30.570 --> 06:32.700
So many people are dying to work there!

06:32.810 --> 06:33.810
And what do you do?

06:34.010 --> 06:35.240
Not only do you not appreciate it,

06:35.240 --> 06:36.190
but you spend all day,

06:36.190 --> 06:37.630
every day, on that crappy script of yours!

06:37.630 --> 06:38.620
Why bother even writing it?

06:38.620 --> 06:39.930
Does anyone actually read it?

06:39.930 --> 06:41.530
You don't understand at all!

06:41.540 --> 06:42.720
I put my heart and soul into it!

06:42.720 --> 06:43.580
Heart and soul?

06:44.250 --> 06:45.300
Once you're fired

06:45.360 --> 06:46.220
and starving,

06:46.659 --> 06:48.190
you won't have either left!

06:48.220 --> 06:48.890
I don't care!

06:48.890 --> 06:49.720
I don't want to keep

06:49.720 --> 06:50.620
flipping those fish

06:50.620 --> 06:51.510
for the rest of my life!

06:51.510 --> 06:52.240
Flipping...

06:52.250 --> 06:53.300
What's wrong with flipping fish?

06:53.300 --> 06:54.330
If you don't...
If you don't want to do it,

06:54.330 --> 06:55.300
what do you want to do?

06:55.300 --> 06:55.890
Tell me!

06:55.950 --> 06:57.170
Get out of my way!

06:57.360 --> 06:59.220
What's wrong with flipping fish?

06:59.330 --> 06:59.870
If you don't flip fish

06:59.870 --> 07:00.980
but rely on...

07:01.100 --> 07:02.230
w-writing scripts,

07:02.300 --> 07:03.540
can you even make a living off it?

07:03.540 --> 07:04.800
How do you know I can't?

07:05.240 --> 07:06.480
I can support myself

07:06.830 --> 07:08.440
and give you a better life!

07:08.720 --> 07:09.120
You...

07:09.220 --> 07:10.470
Give us... Bah!

07:11.810 --> 07:13.560
W-We're living just fine!

07:13.630 --> 07:15.040
We don't need you to worry!

07:15.040 --> 07:15.570
You,

07:15.680 --> 07:17.330
just sort yourself out!

07:17.390 --> 07:18.510
If you make us worry less,

07:18.510 --> 07:20.310
we'll be thanking God, you know?

07:20.390 --> 07:22.190
-Alright, that's enough.
-Always chasing pipe dreams.

07:22.190 --> 07:23.360
Keep talking about writing scripts,

07:23.360 --> 07:24.620
but have you actually written anything
that worked?

07:24.620 --> 07:25.930
You just don't have what it takes!

07:25.930 --> 07:27.300
How many times
have your drafts been sent back?

07:27.300 --> 07:28.130
If you hadn't

07:28.130 --> 07:29.560
neglected your work for writing scripts,

07:29.560 --> 07:31.420
would your superior have criticized you?

07:31.420 --> 07:32.150
And you hit him!

07:32.150 --> 07:33.950
What right do you have to hit him?

07:34.060 --> 07:36.720
You don't know anything,
yet you're blaming me.

07:37.120 --> 07:37.920
I've decided!

07:38.450 --> 07:39.650
I'm going to Beijing!

07:40.070 --> 07:40.890
Where are you going?

07:40.890 --> 07:41.430
Where?

07:41.430 --> 07:42.300
To Beijing!

07:42.430 --> 07:43.930
Do you know what kind of place Beijing is?

07:43.930 --> 07:45.220
What are you going to do there?

07:45.220 --> 07:46.270
Anything—whatever it takes!

07:46.270 --> 07:46.670
You...

07:46.810 --> 07:48.450
You'll starve to death there!

07:48.450 --> 07:49.370
You'll end up begging!

07:49.370 --> 07:50.800
Even if I end up begging on the streets,
that's got nothing to do with you!

07:50.800 --> 07:52.070
Say that again?

07:54.560 --> 07:55.130
Say it!

08:41.289 --> 08:42.690
Mom, I think I can make it.

08:44.820 --> 08:45.750
I believe in you.

08:46.200 --> 08:47.730
You can definitely make it.

08:51.740 --> 08:52.030
Mom,

08:52.030 --> 08:53.700
I really love writing.

08:54.440 --> 08:56.900
And I really want to
give it a shot in Beijing!

08:57.130 --> 08:58.620
I'll check for tickets tomorrow.

08:58.620 --> 08:59.550
Don't tell Dad.

09:10.650 --> 09:11.240
Son...

09:12.870 --> 09:14.130
Since you've decided,

09:14.360 --> 09:15.290
give it your all.

09:23.100 --> 09:24.760
We raised you all these years.

09:25.700 --> 09:26.860
Just don't leave

09:27.770 --> 09:29.340
without saying goodbye.

09:31.360 --> 09:33.000
You go check for tickets tomorrow.

09:33.000 --> 09:34.340
I'll help you pack.

09:44.620 --> 09:45.280
Go to sleep.

09:45.870 --> 09:46.530
Go to sleep.

10:05.960 --> 10:07.060
[Mr. Xu Shengli,
Your essay "Happy New Year"]

10:07.080 --> 10:08.240
[has been selected as one of Yantai's
Top Ten Outstanding Essays.]

10:08.260 --> 10:09.450
[This certificate is awarded
in recognition of this achievement.]

10:09.470 --> 10:10.610
[Mr. Xu Shengli,
Your essay "Stories of a Small Town"]

10:10.630 --> 10:12.120
[has been selected as one of Yantai's
Top Ten Outstanding Essays.]

10:12.140 --> 10:13.910
[This certificate is awarded
in recognition of this achievement.]

10:14.050 --> 10:17.460
[Maritime Scouts]

10:17.460 --> 10:19.380
[A Gathering of Heroes]

10:31.340 --> 10:35.410
[Yantai Station]

10:34.500 --> 10:35.100
I'm fine.

10:35.100 --> 10:36.600
Is the bag too heavy?

10:36.600 --> 10:37.650
No.

10:37.650 --> 10:38.850
It's not heavy at all!

10:39.980 --> 10:41.250
Don't blame your dad.

10:41.460 --> 10:42.000
Last night,

10:42.000 --> 10:44.410
he spent the whole night
packing these bags.

10:44.410 --> 10:45.790
I asked him to come with me
to the station,

10:45.790 --> 10:47.520
but he refused, no matter what—

10:49.110 --> 10:50.110
stubborn as ever.

10:50.720 --> 10:52.650
And you're a chip off the old block.

10:53.600 --> 10:54.730
Actually, I know.

10:56.150 --> 10:57.610
Tell Dad when you get back—

10:58.650 --> 11:00.010
I'll definitely make something

11:00.010 --> 11:00.610
of myself!

11:05.150 --> 11:05.650
Okay.

11:05.750 --> 11:07.000
I know. I know.

11:09.390 --> 11:11.320
I know you're feeling frustrated.

11:11.870 --> 11:12.820
If it really doesn't work out,

11:12.820 --> 11:14.830
just treat it as a trip to Beijing

11:15.220 --> 11:16.280
to clear your mind,

11:16.600 --> 11:17.150
okay?

11:19.150 --> 11:20.170
On the way,

11:20.340 --> 11:21.220
take good care of yourself

11:21.220 --> 11:22.220
and watch your bags.

11:22.220 --> 11:24.150
It's your first time leaving home.

11:24.530 --> 11:27.620
Mom, I'm almost 30.

11:37.390 --> 11:38.450
Alright, alright.

11:38.770 --> 11:40.630
Go on. Everyone else is boarding.

11:42.720 --> 11:43.850
I'm going then, Mom.

11:45.530 --> 11:46.280
Take care.

11:49.630 --> 11:50.630
Mom, go back home.

11:50.770 --> 11:52.060
Get on. Get on.

12:07.610 --> 12:08.450
Excuse me.

12:08.500 --> 12:10.030
Well, I need to put my bag up.

12:11.280 --> 12:13.410
Make sure that the suitcase is secure.

12:16.210 --> 12:16.810
Excuse me.

12:19.220 --> 12:21.100
I put a thermos cup in your bag.

12:21.250 --> 12:22.320
Once the train starts,

12:22.320 --> 12:23.700
go get some hot water.

12:23.790 --> 12:25.510
I know, Mom.

12:26.440 --> 12:28.100
I'll call you when I get there.

12:29.390 --> 12:30.820
Once you're settled, tell me

12:30.820 --> 12:31.620
your address.

12:36.890 --> 12:38.170
Visitors seeing passengers off,

12:38.170 --> 12:39.230
please stand back!

12:39.440 --> 12:40.650
The train is about to depart!

12:40.650 --> 12:41.340
Go back.

12:44.370 --> 12:45.390
Mom, go on back.

12:46.860 --> 12:47.840
Go home. Go home.

12:50.530 --> 12:51.060
Bye-bye.

12:52.510 --> 12:53.120
Bye-bye.

12:54.170 --> 12:55.030
Good luck, son.

12:55.600 --> 12:56.460
I'll do my best.

12:57.410 --> 12:58.140
You can do it.

13:18.120 --> 13:19.300
Hurry back!

14:27.160 --> 14:30.790
[Beijing Station]

14:42.360 --> 14:42.790
Sir,

14:43.360 --> 14:44.390
looking for a place to stay?

14:44.390 --> 14:45.420
My place is huge!

14:45.460 --> 14:46.260
Lots of space,

14:46.360 --> 14:47.010
with big beds, too!

14:46.900 --> 14:47.530
[Jiale Hotel]

14:47.150 --> 14:48.480
The quilts are all brand new.

14:48.480 --> 14:49.330
Soft and fluffy.

14:49.260 --> 14:51.850
[Beijing Station]

14:49.440 --> 14:50.630
Sir, our beds are so comfy—

14:50.630 --> 14:51.940
it's like sleeping on a cloud.

14:51.940 --> 14:53.360
Guaranteed sweet dreams every night.

14:51.990 --> 14:53.390
[Jiale Hotel]

14:53.650 --> 14:54.000
Then,

14:54.000 --> 14:55.170
how much is the rent?

14:56.010 --> 14:56.910
Pay whatever feels right to you.

14:56.910 --> 14:57.920
Whatever you think is fair.

14:57.160 --> 14:57.720
[Jiale Hotel]

14:58.010 --> 14:59.370
Well, let me take you
to check it out first,

14:59.370 --> 14:59.790
okay?

14:59.860 --> 15:00.820
What do you think you're doing?

15:00.820 --> 15:01.840
Ever heard of first come, first served?

15:00.890 --> 15:02.030
[Changxing Hotel]

15:02.000 --> 15:03.440
I saw him first, but I was slow!

15:03.440 --> 15:04.440
Which eye of yours saw him first?

15:04.440 --> 15:05.750
-Sir, come with me.
-Go away!

15:05.040 --> 15:06.540
[Beijing Station]

15:06.030 --> 15:06.390
Sir.

15:06.410 --> 15:07.670
Come on, sir, let's go!

15:07.670 --> 15:09.130
Are you snatching his bag?

15:09.960 --> 15:10.960
What are you doing

15:11.600 --> 15:12.530
in broad daylight?

15:12.530 --> 15:13.840
Where do you think this is?

15:13.840 --> 15:15.650
You think you two can act wild here,

15:15.650 --> 15:17.250
fighting like cats and dogs?

15:17.630 --> 15:18.460
Little Northeasterner,

15:18.460 --> 15:19.320
no one gets on my nerves

15:19.320 --> 15:20.460
like you do.

15:20.460 --> 15:21.270
I'm telling you,

15:21.270 --> 15:22.870
you're not getting a piece of this today!

15:22.870 --> 15:24.100
What's it got to do with you?

15:24.100 --> 15:25.430
You skinny beanpole.

15:25.460 --> 15:25.910
Hurry up.

15:25.570 --> 15:29.040
[Beijing Station]

15:25.910 --> 15:26.770
Scram!

15:27.030 --> 15:27.480
Sir.

15:27.630 --> 15:28.890
Still won't stop, huh?

15:29.500 --> 15:30.700
Am I talking to a wall?

15:30.860 --> 15:31.630
What are you doing?

15:31.630 --> 15:32.510
Dragging and pulling him like that—

15:32.510 --> 15:33.150
just snatching him like goods?

15:33.150 --> 15:34.530
Don't push your luck!

15:34.620 --> 15:35.380
Sir.

15:35.170 --> 15:39.470
[Beijing Station]

15:36.440 --> 15:38.240
The police are right over there!

15:38.340 --> 15:39.600
That little guesthouse operation of yours,

15:39.600 --> 15:40.080
what?

15:40.170 --> 15:41.500
You don't want to stay in business, huh?

15:41.500 --> 15:42.860
What did you say? Say that again!

15:42.860 --> 15:43.320
Come on!

15:43.340 --> 15:45.070
Let's go to the police station!

15:48.700 --> 15:49.860
Fine, Little Northeasterner.

15:49.860 --> 15:50.660
You're tough.

15:51.240 --> 15:52.370
Keep this up!

15:52.600 --> 15:53.740
Just you wait!

15:53.770 --> 15:54.700
I'll be waiting!

15:58.480 --> 16:00.610
Come on, come on, take a look over here!

16:01.840 --> 16:02.440
Thank you.

16:02.840 --> 16:03.500
No problem.

16:03.740 --> 16:04.600
New to Beijing?

16:04.700 --> 16:04.980
Yes.

16:05.000 --> 16:06.010
Need a place to stay?

16:06.010 --> 16:06.480
Yes.

16:06.510 --> 16:08.240
I'd rather look around myself.

16:09.550 --> 16:09.980
My place is close to

16:09.980 --> 16:11.360
the Capital Film Studio!

16:10.290 --> 16:12.070
[Beijing Station]

16:12.130 --> 16:13.390
Just two streets away!

16:15.290 --> 16:16.510
How did you know I was going to

16:16.510 --> 16:17.770
the Capital Film Studio?

16:17.770 --> 16:19.270
You artsy types—

16:19.270 --> 16:21.200
your artistic vibe just radiates!

16:23.440 --> 16:24.840
Which hotel are you from?

16:25.140 --> 16:26.890
[Accommodation] [Seasons Change]
[Accommodation & Reception]

16:25.390 --> 16:26.990
Seasons Change Grand Hotel.

16:27.960 --> 16:28.440
No,

16:28.440 --> 16:29.860
I can't afford a big hotel.

16:29.860 --> 16:31.190
A watermelon looks big—

16:31.200 --> 16:32.650
not to an elephant.

16:33.320 --> 16:34.220
A sesame seed looks tiny—

16:34.220 --> 16:35.460
not to an ant.

16:35.980 --> 16:37.770
You've got an interesting way of talking.

16:37.770 --> 16:38.500
Relativity.

16:38.620 --> 16:39.860
Never mind the theory.

16:39.860 --> 16:41.100
The rent for a bed at my place

16:41.100 --> 16:42.100
is just a few yuan.

16:42.480 --> 16:43.910
You'll definitely like it.

16:43.910 --> 16:44.960
Come on.

16:44.960 --> 16:46.250
I've been checking along the way,

16:46.250 --> 16:47.940
and the rent is either 10 or 15 yuan.

16:47.940 --> 16:48.860
"Just a few yuan"—

16:48.860 --> 16:50.440
how much is the rent exactly?

16:50.440 --> 16:51.820
"A few" means under 10.

16:52.250 --> 16:53.410
Go check out my place!

16:53.410 --> 16:54.600
Perfect fit for someone like you!

16:54.600 --> 16:57.260
If you're not satisfied,
you don't have to stay!

16:57.530 --> 16:58.650
T-Then it's a deal.

16:59.150 --> 17:00.810
I'll just go take a look first,

17:00.840 --> 17:02.500
and I'll decide after I see it!

17:02.510 --> 17:03.890
If it's even one yuan more than you said,

17:03.890 --> 17:04.790
I-I'm leaving.

17:04.790 --> 17:05.720
You can't stop me.

17:05.720 --> 17:09.050
If I wanted to cheat you,
why would I have helped you just now?

17:09.930 --> 17:13.240
[Accommodation] [Seasons Change]
[Accommodation & Reception]

17:13.290 --> 17:16.930
[Welcome to Seasons Change Grand Hotel]

17:16.609 --> 17:17.940
Put your luggage inside.

17:17.940 --> 17:19.200
And wait for me a while.

17:19.329 --> 17:21.250
I'm going to round up a few more guests.

17:21.250 --> 17:21.829
It's not worth the trip

17:21.829 --> 17:22.890
for just one guest.

17:23.140 --> 17:23.520
Okay.

17:23.700 --> 17:24.900
Wait here for me a bit!

17:27.740 --> 17:31.430
[Welcome to Seasons Change Grand Hotel]

17:51.510 --> 17:52.600
Sir, a map, please.

17:54.510 --> 17:55.180
Thanks!

17:54.780 --> 17:55.990
[Beijing Travel & Transportation Map]

18:27.200 --> 18:27.790
Thief!

18:27.830 --> 18:28.760
Stop that thief!

18:41.750 --> 18:42.910
Make way! Make way!

18:43.250 --> 18:43.960
Make way!

18:45.850 --> 18:46.770
Where's my bag?

18:46.830 --> 18:47.630
Hurry, get up!

18:48.880 --> 18:49.950
Where's my bag?

18:50.160 --> 18:50.940
-He stole my bag!
-Stay still!

18:50.940 --> 18:51.510
Stay still!

18:51.510 --> 18:52.920
Officers, he stole my bag!

18:52.920 --> 18:53.850
He stole her bag!

18:54.030 --> 18:54.440
Speak!

18:54.720 --> 18:55.580
Where is my bag?

18:55.830 --> 18:56.610
What are you gonna do about it?

18:55.940 --> 18:59.650
[Household Registration Office]
[Case Handling Office]

18:57.420 --> 18:57.920
Shut up!

19:03.030 --> 19:03.560
Alright.

19:04.200 --> 19:05.180
They are

19:05.290 --> 19:05.940
a gang.

19:06.530 --> 19:08.130
How much cash was in your bag?

19:09.140 --> 19:09.940
Two thousand.

19:10.030 --> 19:10.830
Two thousand?

19:14.700 --> 19:15.500
What on earth?

19:15.880 --> 19:17.680
Why did you carry that much cash?

19:18.350 --> 19:20.950
T-That was for
my living expenses and tuition.

19:21.480 --> 19:22.510
I want to audition
for a song and dance troupe here.

19:22.510 --> 19:23.800
I need to take classes.

19:26.350 --> 19:27.140
Officer...

19:28.290 --> 19:29.220
What should I do?

19:30.140 --> 19:30.770
Here's what we'll do.

19:30.770 --> 19:32.000
Write down your address

19:32.000 --> 19:32.790
and phone number.

19:32.790 --> 19:35.720
If there's any update,
we'll contact you right away.

19:37.570 --> 19:39.500
I haven't found a place to stay yet.

19:39.980 --> 19:42.240
And I don't have a contact number either.

19:46.770 --> 19:48.160
Then what are you going to do now?

19:48.160 --> 19:49.720
How about contacting your family

19:49.720 --> 19:51.350
and asking them to wire some money first?

19:51.350 --> 19:52.140
I can't

19:52.330 --> 19:53.790
tell my family about this.

19:58.110 --> 19:59.750
Now don't panic.

20:01.070 --> 20:01.870
I understand—

20:02.050 --> 20:04.380
it's really not easy
for you out-of-towners

20:04.380 --> 20:05.110
coming here.

20:06.680 --> 20:07.340
In Beijing,

20:08.400 --> 20:09.260
remember this:

20:09.680 --> 20:11.810
if you're in trouble, find the police.

20:11.850 --> 20:13.180
This is the station's number.

20:13.180 --> 20:14.880
Once you've settled somewhere,

20:14.880 --> 20:16.300
call me and let me know.

20:17.010 --> 20:17.720
Okay, okay.

20:18.220 --> 20:19.050
Please, I'm counting on you.

20:19.050 --> 20:20.290
You have to help me find it!

20:20.290 --> 20:20.920
Don't worry.

20:20.920 --> 20:21.920
He won't get away.

20:23.640 --> 20:24.050
Hello?

20:26.570 --> 20:28.030
Okay, I'll be right there.

20:30.700 --> 20:32.760
Alright, stop crying. Calm down now.

20:32.960 --> 20:34.440
This young man here is a good guy.

20:34.440 --> 20:35.640
He stepped in to help.

20:35.680 --> 20:36.350
Nowadays,

20:37.070 --> 20:38.600
there aren't many like you.

20:38.700 --> 20:40.230
It was the right thing to do!

20:40.290 --> 20:41.950
I'm counting on you, Officer!

20:48.140 --> 20:48.740
Thank you.

20:49.500 --> 20:50.360
It was nothing.

20:55.550 --> 20:57.370
[Welcome to Beijing]

20:55.960 --> 20:56.850
Thank you, sir.

20:57.350 --> 20:58.070
Don't mention it.

20:57.370 --> 20:58.890
[Exit]

20:58.250 --> 20:59.710
I didn't really help much.

21:00.290 --> 21:02.390
It's just that your loss is huge.

21:03.380 --> 21:05.580
I'll just have to chalk it up to bad luck.

21:05.680 --> 21:06.550
Do you have any relatives

21:06.550 --> 21:07.790
or friends in Beijing?

21:07.790 --> 21:09.120
Do you have a place to go?

21:09.200 --> 21:09.720
No.

21:14.290 --> 21:15.790
When I arrived at the station,

21:15.790 --> 21:17.240
I noticed there was

21:17.240 --> 21:18.240
a state-run guesthouse over there.

21:18.240 --> 21:19.250
It's only about 10 yuan a day.

21:19.100 --> 21:23.490
[Welcome to Beijing]

21:19.830 --> 21:20.610
How about this—

21:20.610 --> 21:21.740
get settled first.

21:21.830 --> 21:23.030
Then let your family know you're safe.

21:23.030 --> 21:24.140
Take the 50 yuan first.

21:24.140 --> 21:24.600
No need!

21:24.810 --> 21:25.610
I really don't.

21:25.610 --> 21:26.070
No need?

21:26.550 --> 21:27.880
Y-You still have money?

21:27.920 --> 21:29.050
Where will you stay?

21:29.160 --> 21:31.030
Are you going to sleep in the square?

21:31.030 --> 21:32.570
A girl like you out on your own—

21:32.570 --> 21:34.170
your family must be worried.

21:34.480 --> 21:35.550
Get settled first.

21:35.810 --> 21:37.180
Then let your family know you're safe.

21:37.180 --> 21:37.640
Take it.

21:44.000 --> 21:45.660
I'll definitely pay you back.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.610
I'll pay you back tomorrow!

21:47.610 --> 21:48.940
Where would you find me?

21:49.500 --> 21:50.090
I don't even know

21:50.090 --> 21:51.480
where I'll be staying yet.

21:51.480 --> 21:53.480
Then let's meet back here tomorrow!

21:54.850 --> 21:56.920
Really, no need. It's not much.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.900
[Welcome to Beijing]

21:58.110 --> 21:58.570
Sir,

21:58.960 --> 22:01.140
this... may not be worth much,

22:01.440 --> 22:02.260
but take it

22:02.380 --> 22:03.240
as collateral.

22:07.200 --> 22:07.570
Okay.

22:09.310 --> 22:10.010
We're both out here

22:10.010 --> 22:11.550
taking our chances in Beijing.

22:11.550 --> 22:12.180
Take care.

22:13.900 --> 22:14.530
I've got to go.

22:14.530 --> 22:15.900
The car's been waiting for me for a while.

22:15.900 --> 22:16.250
Okay.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.180
Thank you, sir!

22:18.400 --> 22:19.200
It's nothing!

22:19.200 --> 22:20.200
See you tomorrow!

22:42.270 --> 22:43.270
Buddy! Over here!

22:44.290 --> 22:44.740
Sir.

22:45.880 --> 22:47.310
-Where did you go?
-Sorry, sorry.

22:47.310 --> 22:49.070
I already sent some guests to the hotel
and came back.

22:49.070 --> 22:50.270
I thought you'd run off.

22:50.270 --> 22:51.160
No, no, I wouldn't do that.

22:51.160 --> 22:51.960
Hurry up and get in.

22:51.960 --> 22:53.070
It'll be dinner time
by the time we get there.

22:53.070 --> 22:54.130
Alright, alright.

22:54.720 --> 22:55.900
Nice sunglasses!

23:00.730 --> 23:02.740
[Hotel; Seasons Change]

23:11.220 --> 23:12.480
First time in Beijing?

23:12.900 --> 23:13.900
Yeah, first time!

23:14.330 --> 23:16.060
Then you gotta take a good look.

23:16.460 --> 23:17.440
If Beijing

23:16.690 --> 23:18.720
[Long Live the Great Unity
of the People of the World]

23:17.440 --> 23:18.640
is the heart of the nation,

23:18.640 --> 23:19.250
then right here

23:18.720 --> 23:20.550
[Long live the People's Republic of China]

23:19.250 --> 23:20.610
is the very core of that heart.

23:20.610 --> 23:22.540
I love going down Chang'an Avenue.

23:23.010 --> 23:24.660
I just love looking at Chairman Mao.

23:24.660 --> 23:25.740
Seeing him makes me happy.

23:25.740 --> 23:26.540
Are you happy?

23:26.610 --> 23:27.810
I'm happy.

23:31.110 --> 23:33.610
[Hotel; Seasons Change]

23:46.920 --> 23:48.980
Your stuff! Don't forget your stuff!

23:50.510 --> 23:50.960
Let me check

23:50.960 --> 23:52.420
if I left anything behind.

23:55.740 --> 23:57.660
Little Northeasterner, you're back.

23:57.660 --> 23:58.320
Having fun?

24:06.740 --> 24:07.940
This is Luogu Hutong!

24:08.720 --> 24:10.120
We're living in a hutong?

24:10.240 --> 24:10.940
They're all

24:10.940 --> 24:12.000
shared courtyards in the hutongs.

24:12.000 --> 24:13.200
Ours is a two-courtyard house.

24:13.200 --> 24:15.260
Look at the gate. It's centuries old!

24:15.270 --> 24:16.000
Back in the day,

24:16.000 --> 24:17.240
only princes or nobles could live here.

24:17.240 --> 24:19.050
Now ordinary folks like us
can live here too.

24:19.050 --> 24:19.580
Wang,

24:19.750 --> 24:20.770
tending your flowers?

24:20.770 --> 24:22.160
Northeasterner, come look at my flowers!

24:22.160 --> 24:23.000
How are they?

24:23.410 --> 24:24.290
I remember this one

24:24.290 --> 24:25.310
hadn't bloomed yesterday.

24:25.310 --> 24:26.510
It just opened today.

24:26.660 --> 24:27.920
I'll snatch one later.

24:27.920 --> 24:29.500
Don't you dare!

24:31.030 --> 24:32.980
One of our old neighbors.
Really interesting guy.

24:32.980 --> 24:34.280
Ma, cooking alone?

24:34.810 --> 24:36.200
My wife hasn't come back yet.

24:36.200 --> 24:37.140
Gotta have a couple of drinks then.

24:37.140 --> 24:38.500
Absolutely. Come by when you have time.

24:38.500 --> 24:39.900
Little Northeasterner,

24:40.250 --> 24:41.420
I've been waiting for you.

24:41.420 --> 24:42.350
What for?

24:42.550 --> 24:43.310
Didn't you say that

24:43.310 --> 24:45.570
my braised pork yesterday was too salty?

24:45.570 --> 24:47.170
I just mentioned it offhand.

24:47.420 --> 24:48.400
Try it again today

24:48.400 --> 24:49.860
and see how I did this time.

24:49.940 --> 24:50.900
Why don't you have a bite too?

24:50.900 --> 24:52.100
No thanks, I'll pass.

24:52.270 --> 24:53.790
Hurry up, come on.

24:53.790 --> 24:54.720
Then, go straight ahead.

24:54.720 --> 24:55.700
See that sign ahead?

24:55.700 --> 24:56.360
Turn right.

24:56.940 --> 24:58.050
I'll meet you out front in a minute.

24:58.050 --> 24:58.420
Okay.

24:58.750 --> 24:59.570
Let me try the pork.

24:59.570 --> 25:00.610
-Come on.
-Let me.

25:01.380 --> 25:01.890
How is it?

25:01.820 --> 25:07.670
[Seasons Change Hotel]

25:02.380 --> 25:04.240
It's not salty today. A bit sweet.

25:04.640 --> 25:05.680
Yesterday too salty, today too sweet,

25:05.680 --> 25:06.140
huh?

25:06.290 --> 25:07.610
You're so picky.

25:20.610 --> 25:21.220
Uncle,

25:21.460 --> 25:23.190
why are you filming the hutong?

25:23.220 --> 25:24.820
The scenery's so beautiful.

25:25.460 --> 25:27.250
You're here to stay at the hotel, right?

25:27.250 --> 25:28.270
It's in there.

25:28.830 --> 25:29.680
Okay, thanks.

25:29.680 --> 25:30.290
Here.

25:30.420 --> 25:30.950
Hee-yur.

25:30.980 --> 25:32.510
It's "Here," not "Hee-yur."

25:32.510 --> 25:33.740
Look at here!

25:33.830 --> 25:34.510
Here!

25:34.720 --> 25:35.840
H-e-r-e,

25:35.860 --> 25:36.660
Here!

25:36.680 --> 25:37.770
Hee-yur.

25:37.790 --> 25:38.460
Here.

25:38.460 --> 25:40.720
What's with all this "Here" and "Hee-yur"?

25:40.720 --> 25:42.220
Uncle, look at this word.

25:42.310 --> 25:44.640
Should we pronounce "Here" or "Hee-yur"?

25:44.720 --> 25:45.700
Here.

25:45.920 --> 25:47.310
H-e-r-e, Here!

25:47.460 --> 25:49.360
Right. H-e-r-e, Here.

25:49.920 --> 25:50.920
Hee-yur.

25:51.330 --> 25:52.880
-Here.
-Are you a local here?

25:52.880 --> 25:53.770
No, I'm not.

25:54.810 --> 25:56.770
Let me teach you a Beijing phrase then.

25:56.770 --> 25:57.830
Sure.

25:57.900 --> 25:59.230
Mind your own business.

25:59.980 --> 26:01.780
Fine, I won't.

26:01.900 --> 26:03.740
The whole courtyard could hear you.

26:03.740 --> 26:04.800
What are you doing?

26:05.570 --> 26:06.290
Who are you?

26:07.090 --> 26:08.690
I'm here to stay at the hotel.

26:08.980 --> 26:09.610
"Seasons Change"?

26:09.610 --> 26:10.010
Right.

26:10.160 --> 26:10.820
Over there.

26:11.090 --> 26:11.550
Thanks.

26:11.830 --> 26:13.250
What's all this "here" or "there"?

26:13.250 --> 26:15.030
Is it "Here" or "Hee-yur"?

26:15.570 --> 26:16.390
Hee-yur.

26:16.700 --> 26:17.300
Young man!

26:19.770 --> 26:20.830
Where are you from?

26:21.030 --> 26:22.090
Yantai, Shandong.

26:22.790 --> 26:23.790
By the sea, right?

26:24.750 --> 26:25.610
How old are you?

26:26.000 --> 26:26.730
Twenty-six.

26:28.830 --> 26:29.760
Came here alone?

26:31.310 --> 26:31.920
I'm

26:32.050 --> 26:33.660
the head of
the Neighborhood Committee here.

26:33.660 --> 26:34.460
Hello, hello.

26:34.530 --> 26:35.790
Since you're new here,

26:36.090 --> 26:37.890
you must register with us first.

26:38.790 --> 26:40.720
For national peace and stability,

26:40.750 --> 26:41.150
right?

26:41.440 --> 26:42.720
Law and order, the long-term security,

26:42.720 --> 26:44.120
depend on every one of us.

26:44.240 --> 26:44.680
Understood!

26:44.680 --> 26:45.080
Right?

26:46.070 --> 26:47.530
Go register with us first.

26:47.940 --> 26:49.000
Who brought you here?

26:49.000 --> 26:49.980
Little Northeasterner.

26:49.980 --> 26:51.220
Where is he then?

26:51.740 --> 26:52.070
He...

26:52.110 --> 26:52.840
Director Li!

26:52.960 --> 26:54.890
How did this end up disturbing you?

26:55.140 --> 26:56.840
He's new here.

26:57.240 --> 26:57.640
You...

26:57.720 --> 26:58.750
You let him wander around alone.

26:58.750 --> 26:59.980
If something happens,
will you take responsibility?

26:59.980 --> 27:00.920
Wang Yunfang insisted I

27:00.920 --> 27:02.120
try her braised pork.

27:02.510 --> 27:03.940
Besides, with you watching over here,

27:03.940 --> 27:05.050
the security in this area

27:04.850 --> 27:08.570
[Seasons Change Hotel]

27:05.050 --> 27:06.310
is famously good.

27:06.350 --> 27:07.610
You and your sweet talk!

27:07.610 --> 27:08.330
I'm telling you,

27:08.330 --> 27:09.240
stop making me worry about you

27:09.240 --> 27:10.070
all the time.

27:10.330 --> 27:10.880
Remember to register.

27:10.880 --> 27:11.610
Don't worry.

27:11.720 --> 27:13.050
Go back and have dinner.

27:13.500 --> 27:14.360
Leave him to me.

27:14.960 --> 27:15.560
This is it!

27:16.010 --> 27:17.270
Seasons Change Hotel.

27:18.200 --> 27:19.680
In all of old Beijing,

27:20.180 --> 27:21.220
you won't find

27:21.030 --> 27:30.280
[Seasons Change Hotel]

27:21.270 --> 27:23.000
a courtyard this comfortable!

27:32.920 --> 27:34.320
I live in this gate lodge.

27:34.460 --> 27:35.660
There's a phone here.

27:35.790 --> 27:36.590
The front gate

27:36.590 --> 27:38.180
locks every night at 11.

27:38.240 --> 27:39.180
If you come back late,

27:39.180 --> 27:40.330
don't blame me for not letting you in.

27:40.330 --> 27:40.700
Okay.

27:41.830 --> 27:42.700
We have a new guest?

27:42.700 --> 27:43.100
Hello.

27:43.310 --> 27:45.090
Whose stinky shoes are in the hallway?

27:45.090 --> 27:46.220
What's wrong, guys?

27:46.350 --> 27:46.740
Luo,

27:46.830 --> 27:47.700
didn't you say nothing should be left in

27:47.700 --> 27:48.500
common areas?

27:48.530 --> 27:49.610
I'm clearing it all out today.

27:49.610 --> 27:50.330
Hurry up.

27:51.070 --> 27:51.420
Alright.

27:51.420 --> 27:52.750
Clear out the fire exit.

27:53.030 --> 27:53.900
People living here come

27:53.900 --> 27:54.960
from every corner of the country.

27:54.960 --> 27:56.000
North, south, all around.

27:56.000 --> 27:57.660
Some are here
visiting relatives or friends.

27:57.660 --> 27:59.380
There're also tourists,
business travelers,

27:59.380 --> 28:00.720
fortune seekers, and dreamers.

28:00.720 --> 28:01.920
Fate brought us

28:01.920 --> 28:02.660
together.

28:03.140 --> 28:04.070
After living here for a while,

28:04.070 --> 28:05.160
we've become like family.

28:05.160 --> 28:05.570
Look.

28:06.030 --> 28:07.070
This area

28:07.200 --> 28:08.060
is for cooking.

28:08.680 --> 28:09.790
Everyone cooks together.

28:09.790 --> 28:10.520
Isn't it fun?

28:11.350 --> 28:12.480
What are you making?

28:12.480 --> 28:13.880
Pork with chili peppers.

28:14.160 --> 28:15.420
Isn't this a cold dish?

28:15.500 --> 28:16.750
I'm preparing to make it.

28:16.750 --> 28:17.440
Fried sauce noodles?

28:17.440 --> 28:17.850
Right.

28:18.010 --> 28:18.340
Okay.

28:18.740 --> 28:19.980
Save a bowl for me today,

28:19.980 --> 28:20.250
is that okay?

28:20.250 --> 28:20.850
You got it.

28:20.900 --> 28:22.090
Next time I cook, I'll save you a bowl.

28:22.090 --> 28:22.500
Okay.

28:23.000 --> 28:24.460
You provide the noodles,
and I'll bring the garlic!

28:24.460 --> 28:24.990
Alright.

28:26.030 --> 28:26.480
We have

28:26.640 --> 28:28.050
24-hour hot water!

28:28.590 --> 28:30.700
This water isn't hot enough
to make instant noodles!

28:30.700 --> 28:32.200
It takes time to boil, eh?

28:32.830 --> 28:34.460
Get yourself a thermos bottle later.

28:34.460 --> 28:35.400
When there is hot water,

28:35.400 --> 28:36.420
just store some, and you're set.

28:36.420 --> 28:36.750
Okay.

28:37.610 --> 28:39.270
Here! Women's bathroom!

28:40.460 --> 28:41.850
There, the men's bathroom!

28:41.850 --> 28:43.310
You can wash clothes here.

28:44.460 --> 28:46.240
Come on, girls,

28:46.250 --> 28:47.830
once the clothes are dry, take them down!

28:47.830 --> 28:48.880
Don't leave them hanging
all over the place!

28:48.880 --> 28:50.500
It bothers me, you know?

28:51.460 --> 28:52.250
We've been a "model sanitation unit"

28:52.250 --> 28:52.940
every year!

28:53.000 --> 28:54.400
Don't mess that up for me!

28:55.660 --> 28:56.030
Sis,

28:56.050 --> 28:56.830
I'm talking here.

28:56.830 --> 28:58.090
Can you do your vocalizing later?

28:58.090 --> 28:59.140
Thank you, sis.

29:00.500 --> 29:02.880
Small but fully equipped.

29:03.240 --> 29:05.090
That little courtyard upstairs
looks small, right?

29:05.090 --> 29:07.110
Big enough to run a racehorse ragged.

29:07.110 --> 29:08.220
And even down in the basement,

29:08.220 --> 29:10.350
a thousand-year pine could take root.

29:10.400 --> 29:11.130
On that side—

29:11.180 --> 29:12.710
there're 28 rooms in total.

29:13.330 --> 29:14.070
Keep moving

29:14.290 --> 29:14.980
and turn left—

29:14.980 --> 29:16.110
there's a fire exit.

29:21.850 --> 29:22.880
This way, this way!

29:22.880 --> 29:24.680
You're not staying on that side!

29:27.960 --> 29:28.480
See?

29:29.460 --> 29:31.260
Room 108—"fortune all the way."

29:31.510 --> 29:32.310
Lucky, right?

29:32.610 --> 29:33.440
Very lucky.

29:33.610 --> 29:34.110
Well.

29:35.090 --> 29:35.690
Here we go.

29:37.740 --> 29:39.380
Everyone who comes to Beijing

29:39.380 --> 29:40.710
wants to put down roots.

29:40.960 --> 29:41.680
But that's all talk

29:41.680 --> 29:43.540
until you've found your footing.

29:43.880 --> 29:45.250
Beijing is enormous.

29:45.830 --> 29:46.770
If you can just have a place

29:46.770 --> 29:48.000
and a bed of your own,

29:48.250 --> 29:49.440
you'll feel secure.

29:49.480 --> 29:49.800
Yes.

29:49.960 --> 29:50.880
Everyone in this room

29:50.880 --> 29:52.140
is in the arts.

29:52.700 --> 29:53.500
This guy in this bed...

29:53.500 --> 29:54.100
Come look.

29:55.590 --> 29:56.450
Great painter!

29:57.160 --> 29:57.960
In the making.

29:58.640 --> 30:00.170
From Shanxi. Name's Cao Ye.

30:00.700 --> 30:02.700
He's a bit eccentric.

30:03.420 --> 30:04.480
Look at the pets he keeps.

30:04.480 --> 30:06.510
They're different from everyone else's.

30:06.510 --> 30:07.970
And this one in this bed...

30:08.500 --> 30:09.230
A Beijinger!

30:10.850 --> 30:11.720
Tao Liangliang.

30:11.720 --> 30:12.790
I call him Mr. Tao.

30:13.200 --> 30:14.130
He's a musician—

30:14.550 --> 30:15.750
plays the saxophone.

30:16.010 --> 30:18.380
He's been trying to get into
a song and dance troupe.

30:18.380 --> 30:20.070
Wait, he... he's a Beijinger.

30:20.140 --> 30:21.420
Why is he staying here then?

30:21.420 --> 30:21.950
See that?

30:22.220 --> 30:23.420
Even a born-and-bred Beijinger stays here.

30:23.420 --> 30:25.070
That's enough to show
it's comfortable here.

30:25.070 --> 30:25.800
A good place.

30:26.830 --> 30:27.890
The man in this bed—

30:28.610 --> 30:29.550
he's from Henan.

30:29.830 --> 30:30.960
Name's Guo Zongbao.

30:31.570 --> 30:32.250
I hear he used to

30:32.250 --> 30:33.180
perform Henan opera.

30:33.180 --> 30:34.180
Now he's an actor.

30:34.920 --> 30:35.720
An actor?

30:36.110 --> 30:37.010
An extra, though.

30:37.010 --> 30:38.420
Occasionally gets a few lines.

30:38.420 --> 30:39.680
That's still an actor!

30:39.720 --> 30:40.310
Exactly!

30:41.140 --> 30:42.440
This is your bed!

30:44.030 --> 30:44.550
But... but...

30:44.550 --> 30:45.920
what about all this stuff?

30:45.920 --> 30:47.050
Move these things away,

30:47.050 --> 30:49.380
and your bed is
exactly the same as theirs.

30:50.900 --> 30:52.700
Alright, you've seen the place.

30:54.030 --> 30:54.790
This bed—

30:55.570 --> 30:57.290
six yuan a day.

30:59.240 --> 31:01.170
Rent is paid every 10 days minimum.

31:01.720 --> 31:03.110
Forty yuan for the deposit.

31:03.110 --> 31:04.140
When it's almost due,

31:04.140 --> 31:05.540
I'll remind you to renew.

31:07.050 --> 31:09.530
Anyway, if you don't want me nagging...

31:15.550 --> 31:15.920
Okay.

31:16.880 --> 31:17.940
Straightforward.

31:19.270 --> 31:20.640
You'll definitely

31:21.030 --> 31:22.050
strike some sparks

31:22.050 --> 31:23.250
living with this lot.

31:23.570 --> 31:24.830
What do you mean?

31:25.090 --> 31:26.290
Just let it sink in.

31:26.590 --> 31:27.590
After you move in,

31:27.610 --> 31:28.740
you can mull it over.

31:30.010 --> 31:31.140
Alright, that's it.

31:31.220 --> 31:31.660
Wait.

31:36.920 --> 31:38.200
This is a specialty from my hometown!

31:38.200 --> 31:38.660
Take it.

31:38.750 --> 31:40.400
Well, I can't accept it.

31:40.400 --> 31:40.900
Take it.

31:41.240 --> 31:43.940
-We just met—how can I accept your gift?
-It's fine.

31:43.940 --> 31:45.670
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

31:46.400 --> 31:46.930
Alright.

31:47.290 --> 31:48.550
As the seasons change,

31:49.030 --> 31:50.880
may your dreams come true!

31:51.480 --> 31:52.880
My dreams will come true!

31:54.310 --> 31:55.550
Come up and register in a bit!

31:55.550 --> 31:56.080
Alright!

31:58.770 --> 31:59.830
Don't worry, Mom.

32:00.200 --> 32:02.060
I'm staying at a state-run hotel.

32:03.900 --> 32:05.300
The place is really nice.

32:07.250 --> 32:09.180
You didn't even bring many things.

32:09.400 --> 32:10.810
Go buy yourself some clothes

32:09.480 --> 32:14.050
[Nanpin General Store]

32:11.090 --> 32:12.480
and eat whatever you want.

32:12.480 --> 32:14.080
Don't worry about the money.

32:14.660 --> 32:15.880
Why didn't you take the new clothes

32:15.880 --> 32:17.000
I made for you?

32:17.440 --> 32:18.970
I'll mail them to you later.

32:19.610 --> 32:20.340
Don't worry.

32:20.610 --> 32:21.830
There's a customer waiting in the shop.

32:21.830 --> 32:22.680
I have to go.

32:24.590 --> 32:26.090
Sis, I'm off!

32:25.290 --> 32:28.260
[Nanpin General Store]

32:26.200 --> 32:26.800
Thank you.

32:28.370 --> 32:30.940
[Cai's Clothing Shop]

32:30.940 --> 32:32.310
[Meiqin's Tailor Shop]

32:32.290 --> 32:34.240
Sorry to keep you waiting.

32:34.330 --> 32:35.810
Went to call Zhuang Zhuang?

32:35.810 --> 32:36.240
Yes.

32:36.810 --> 32:37.420
What's wrong with the coat?

32:37.420 --> 32:37.880
Zhuang,

32:38.090 --> 32:38.740
I want to alter

32:38.740 --> 32:39.880
this coat again.

32:40.010 --> 32:40.880
Look at the collar—

32:40.880 --> 32:41.830
can you change it

32:42.220 --> 32:43.020
to that style?

32:45.810 --> 32:46.350
Sure.

32:47.500 --> 32:48.770
Let me take your measurements again.

32:48.770 --> 32:49.160
Okay.

32:50.830 --> 32:52.360
I've made a few new designs.

32:52.380 --> 32:53.550
I think they'll suit you well.

32:53.550 --> 32:55.110
Do you want to try them on later?

32:55.110 --> 32:55.840
Another day.

32:58.240 --> 33:00.300
I have to say, you're really blessed.

33:00.850 --> 33:02.580
Second marriages aren't easy.

33:03.500 --> 33:04.770
Zhuang Zhuang has all grown up now.

33:04.770 --> 33:06.700
She's even made her way to Beijing.

33:07.350 --> 33:07.980
Ye!

33:13.220 --> 33:14.590
I've put the uniforms for Factory No. 6

33:14.590 --> 33:15.500
on the counter.

33:15.550 --> 33:16.290
Sort them by size

33:16.290 --> 33:17.620
and deliver them later.

33:18.280 --> 33:19.430
I'll be going now.

33:19.740 --> 33:20.270
Alright.

33:20.460 --> 33:20.980
Okay, take care.

33:20.980 --> 33:21.350
Okay.

33:21.380 --> 33:25.070
[Meiqin's Tailor Shop]

33:21.810 --> 33:22.410
Take care.

33:23.590 --> 33:24.310
Take care.

33:24.330 --> 33:24.700
Bye.

33:27.090 --> 33:27.660
Girl,

33:27.960 --> 33:30.090
it's not good to
lie to your family like that.

33:30.090 --> 33:31.550
If you were my own daughter,

33:31.550 --> 33:32.680
I'd be worried sick.

33:33.030 --> 33:34.140
If my mom knew

33:34.140 --> 33:35.470
all my money was stolen,

33:36.010 --> 33:37.470
she'd be worried sick too.

33:40.240 --> 33:42.050
Then... have you decided

33:42.050 --> 33:43.510
what kind of room you want?

33:46.140 --> 33:48.790
[Standard Double Room]
[Standard Single Room]

33:47.720 --> 33:48.250
Ma'am,

33:48.740 --> 33:49.960
do you have

33:49.960 --> 33:51.090
any beds available

33:51.090 --> 33:52.330
in the standard quadruple rooms?

33:52.330 --> 33:53.140
No, all full.

33:53.400 --> 33:54.250
The cheapest one right now

33:54.250 --> 33:55.420
is the one for 20.

34:04.220 --> 34:05.010
Ma'am, could you tell me—

34:05.010 --> 34:05.900
are there any places nearby

34:05.900 --> 34:07.290
where I can find odd jobs?

34:07.290 --> 34:08.380
I'll do anything.

34:08.550 --> 34:10.150
There's a street in the back.

34:10.150 --> 34:12.260
It's got... small bookstores,

34:13.400 --> 34:14.150
barbershops,

34:14.150 --> 34:14.949
snack stalls,

34:15.110 --> 34:16.770
general stores—everything.

34:16.820 --> 34:18.030
They're hiring temp workers every day.

34:18.030 --> 34:19.630
Why don't you go check it out?

34:19.840 --> 34:20.300
Okay.

34:20.510 --> 34:22.400
So, do you still want to stay here?

34:24.820 --> 34:26.030
I won't stay today.

34:26.530 --> 34:27.230
I'm going to see

34:27.230 --> 34:28.830
if I can find some work first.

34:29.530 --> 34:30.400
Oh, right, ma'am.

34:30.400 --> 34:31.900
Here's the money for the call.

34:31.900 --> 34:32.830
No need, no need.

34:33.010 --> 34:34.469
Pay me after you find a job.

34:34.840 --> 34:36.340
It's fine. Go ahead.

34:38.460 --> 34:39.060
Thank you.

34:42.800 --> 34:43.460
Come on, Liangliang.

34:43.460 --> 34:45.440
Turning his bed over
is going a bit far, isn't it?

34:45.440 --> 34:46.050
Zongbao,

34:46.070 --> 34:48.600
he just can't go around
bullying Heretic Cao!

34:56.260 --> 34:57.090
L-Looking for something?

34:57.090 --> 34:58.350
L-Let me help you guys!

35:03.340 --> 35:04.940
Nothing to look for anymore?

35:08.920 --> 35:10.320
You ruined the painting?

35:12.350 --> 35:13.210
I'm really sorry.

35:13.210 --> 35:14.260
I accidentally

35:14.260 --> 35:15.340
ruined this painting.

35:15.340 --> 35:15.670
Um...

35:15.670 --> 35:17.150
Um... Let me introduce myself.

35:17.150 --> 35:18.350
My name is Xu Shengli.

35:18.570 --> 35:20.010
I'm from Yantai, Shandong.

35:20.010 --> 35:21.900
I was removing all that stuff from my bed

35:21.900 --> 35:22.650
and accidentally

35:22.650 --> 35:23.850
ruined the painting.

35:24.130 --> 35:25.400
I just went out to buy some tape.

35:25.400 --> 35:25.960
I thought

35:26.230 --> 35:27.380
I could tape it back together.

35:27.380 --> 35:28.240
It can be fixed.

35:28.730 --> 35:29.660
What did you say?

35:31.590 --> 35:33.320
You want to tape this painting?

35:34.360 --> 35:34.960
Have you heard of

35:34.960 --> 35:36.070
the "Mona Lisa"?

35:37.130 --> 35:37.930
Y-Yes, I have.

35:38.010 --> 35:38.810
This painting

35:39.480 --> 35:40.570
was created by me,

35:40.590 --> 35:41.210
Cao Ye.

35:41.480 --> 35:42.680
"Running Wang Erya"!

35:43.380 --> 35:43.900
Now,

35:44.780 --> 35:46.360
you messed up her legs like this.

35:46.360 --> 35:48.090
How is Erya supposed to run now?

35:48.940 --> 35:49.400
Look...

35:49.840 --> 35:50.840
Well, I...

35:50.840 --> 35:52.170
I want to use the tape...

35:52.300 --> 35:53.160
Use the tape...

35:54.460 --> 35:55.440
I want to tape it

35:55.780 --> 35:56.500
from the back!

35:56.500 --> 35:58.730
You wouldn't see anything from the front.

35:58.730 --> 36:00.530
It's not about the front or back!

36:00.710 --> 36:02.040
Do you even know who I am?

36:02.320 --> 36:04.210
Do you know
how much this painting is worth?

36:04.210 --> 36:06.010
Have you ever walked into a gallery
and seen

36:06.010 --> 36:07.380
a painting held together with tape?

36:07.380 --> 36:09.340
You ruined my painting!

36:14.420 --> 36:14.880
Well...

36:15.860 --> 36:17.320
Look, sir, how about this?

36:17.510 --> 36:18.630
How much is your painting?

36:18.630 --> 36:19.510
I'll pay for it.

36:20.960 --> 36:22.820
Worth a fortune—try and pay that!

36:24.530 --> 36:25.590
Why are you smiling?

36:25.590 --> 36:26.520
What's so funny?

36:26.980 --> 36:27.880
You ruined my painting,

36:27.880 --> 36:29.110
and now you're insulting me too?

36:29.110 --> 36:30.440
I... I didn't.

36:30.570 --> 36:31.230
You didn't?

36:31.380 --> 36:31.800
No, no...

36:31.800 --> 36:33.130
Then pay me 80,000 yuan!

36:36.480 --> 36:36.900
Cao.

36:37.900 --> 36:39.500
That's a bit too much, right?

36:43.800 --> 36:45.150
Sir, that's

36:45.150 --> 36:46.420
bordering on extortion, right?

36:46.420 --> 36:46.960
What?

36:47.400 --> 36:48.730
What do you mean, "extortion"?

36:48.730 --> 36:50.170
You ruined the painting,

36:50.170 --> 36:51.190
and now you're insulting my buddy!

36:51.190 --> 36:52.440
What do you want?

36:52.440 --> 36:53.900
Liangliang, Liangliang!

36:57.840 --> 36:58.460
Brother

36:59.300 --> 37:01.000
from Yantai,

37:01.670 --> 37:02.670
every place

37:03.190 --> 37:05.090
has its rules.

37:05.650 --> 37:08.340
Without rules, there's no order.

37:08.780 --> 37:10.550
What we say is the rules!

37:10.650 --> 37:12.170
The rules are what we say!

37:12.210 --> 37:13.280
You didn't check what kind of place

37:13.280 --> 37:14.440
Room 108 is first?

37:14.440 --> 37:14.920
You think

37:14.920 --> 37:16.320
you can just move in here?

37:16.340 --> 37:17.440
This is just a hostel!

37:17.440 --> 37:18.360
I rented a bed.

37:18.590 --> 37:19.840
That makes it mine.

37:20.170 --> 37:21.050
There was stuff on it,

37:21.050 --> 37:22.280
so I had to move it!

37:22.320 --> 37:23.150
And I accidentally damaged

37:23.150 --> 37:24.400
your painting in the process!

37:24.400 --> 37:25.530
I apologized to you.

37:25.630 --> 37:27.360
And I said I could pay you for it.

37:27.530 --> 37:28.590
What other rules are there?

37:28.590 --> 37:29.760
"What other rules?"

37:29.800 --> 37:31.190
If you're a tiger, hide your claws;

37:31.190 --> 37:32.980
if you're a dragon, keep your head down!

37:32.980 --> 37:34.130
That's the rule!

37:34.190 --> 37:35.820
"If you're a tiger, hide your claws."

37:35.820 --> 37:37.690
Some tiger—really good at backing down.

37:37.690 --> 37:38.440
What do you mean by that?

37:38.440 --> 37:39.900
Liangliang, Liangliang!

37:40.920 --> 37:41.450
Back off.

37:41.460 --> 37:41.880
You...

37:45.150 --> 37:47.820
Brother from Yantai,

37:48.800 --> 37:51.150
you're being a bit arrogant here.

37:51.500 --> 37:52.280
Do you know

37:52.690 --> 37:54.500
what happened to the last guy

37:54.510 --> 37:56.440
who got cocky with us

37:56.440 --> 37:57.280
in this room?

37:57.320 --> 37:58.650
He's still on crutches!

37:58.670 --> 38:01.000
With a urine bag
dangling from one of them!

38:01.960 --> 38:02.480
I see.

38:03.480 --> 38:04.210
Understood.

38:05.150 --> 38:05.800
Sir, I...

38:06.110 --> 38:07.510
once again, I apologize.

38:07.840 --> 38:08.570
I apologize.

38:09.000 --> 38:10.930
Think about how much this painting

38:11.000 --> 38:11.880
is really worth

38:12.280 --> 38:13.170
and name a price.

38:13.170 --> 38:14.230
I'll pay you for it.

38:14.440 --> 38:15.570
Rest assured, guys.

38:15.860 --> 38:16.650
I won't be

38:16.940 --> 38:18.400
staying in this room long.

38:20.010 --> 38:20.590
And I won't

38:20.590 --> 38:21.920
cause you any more trouble.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.250
I usually go to bed late.

38:23.480 --> 38:24.670
I'll head out for a walk.

38:24.670 --> 38:26.000
You guys go to bed first.

38:41.630 --> 38:43.690
This is a specialty from my hometown.

38:44.460 --> 38:45.320
Please, try it.

38:51.820 --> 38:53.480
What, never seen food before?

38:55.530 --> 38:57.150
This goes great with booze!

38:57.400 --> 38:59.110
Why were you holding me back?

38:59.210 --> 39:00.600
I'm furious!

39:00.840 --> 39:02.040
I want to kick his ass!

39:03.510 --> 39:04.980
I'm furious!

39:12.320 --> 39:12.920
Have some.

39:13.230 --> 39:13.840
Calm down.

39:14.480 --> 39:15.760
Get lost. Now.

39:20.890 --> 39:25.520
[Seasons Change Hotel]

39:25.520 --> 39:28.030
[Guest Room]

39:30.300 --> 39:31.900
Why are you two sitting here?

39:31.940 --> 39:32.870
Waiting for you.

39:33.900 --> 39:34.440
Look.

39:41.300 --> 39:42.530
Do what you have to do.

39:46.900 --> 39:47.320
Done.

39:47.980 --> 39:49.090
It's useless.

39:49.230 --> 39:50.130
How is it useless?

39:50.130 --> 39:50.630
Watch.

39:50.800 --> 39:53.110
Three, two, one.

39:55.960 --> 39:57.570
See? It didn't work.

39:59.170 --> 40:00.650
Must be the wrong method.

40:01.630 --> 40:03.290
What trick should we use then?

40:04.880 --> 40:05.920
It's no use!

40:05.960 --> 40:06.460
Look.

40:12.170 --> 40:13.430
Well, what do we do now?

40:13.820 --> 40:16.020
No wonder he said we should sleep first.

40:16.440 --> 40:18.900
Can't believe someone
can snore that badly.

40:19.440 --> 40:20.970
He's an honest man, though.

40:21.230 --> 40:22.960
What, now you're praising him?

40:22.980 --> 40:25.130
If there's a problem,
it should be treated.

40:25.130 --> 40:25.790
Watch this.

40:36.190 --> 40:36.850
He's awake.

40:37.190 --> 40:37.630
Man,

40:38.380 --> 40:39.820
you were snoring!

40:40.730 --> 40:41.920
Don't fall asleep yet.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.380
Wait until we're asleep first,

40:43.380 --> 40:43.900
okay?

40:43.900 --> 40:45.070
Get up and stay awake for a bit.

40:45.070 --> 40:46.090
You guys sleep. You guys sleep.

40:46.090 --> 40:47.020
You sleep first.

40:52.440 --> 40:53.500
He's out that fast?

40:54.000 --> 40:54.860
Make him sit up!

40:55.570 --> 40:57.760
Lift him. One, two, three. Up you go.

40:59.880 --> 41:01.110
Don't fall asleep yet!

41:01.110 --> 41:01.840
Wake up a bit!

41:02.380 --> 41:03.590
You two go to sleep.

41:03.880 --> 41:05.620
I'll handle things here.

41:06.130 --> 41:07.130
Let's have a chat.

41:07.820 --> 41:08.300
Sorry.

41:09.110 --> 41:09.710
It's okay.

41:10.170 --> 41:10.940
It's just...

41:11.670 --> 41:12.240
If you...

41:57.280 --> 41:57.980
Mr. Tao,

41:57.980 --> 41:59.500
I thought it was an earthquake.

41:59.500 --> 42:00.550
If you smash my glass top,

42:00.550 --> 42:01.030
it'll break,

42:01.030 --> 42:02.090
and you'll get cut.

42:02.300 --> 42:03.730
What? What brings you here...

42:03.730 --> 42:04.460
at this hour?

42:04.500 --> 42:06.430
Can you kick that guy out of my room?

42:06.650 --> 42:07.580
He offended you?

42:08.570 --> 42:09.460
He snores.

42:10.420 --> 42:11.220
I can't sleep.

42:11.530 --> 42:13.330
Not just me. None of us can sleep.

42:13.530 --> 42:14.900
If he snores, just whistle.

42:14.900 --> 42:16.210
Whistle, my foot.

42:16.210 --> 42:17.410
I play the saxophone.

42:17.690 --> 42:18.980
But we can't kick someone out

42:18.980 --> 42:19.880
just for snoring.

42:19.880 --> 42:21.400
Who doesn't snore when they sleep?

42:21.400 --> 42:22.000
This is...

42:22.070 --> 42:23.600
Will you kick him out or not?

42:24.280 --> 42:25.940
You're putting me on the spot.

42:25.960 --> 42:27.360
Didn't you say you were tight on cash?

42:27.360 --> 42:28.560
A friend gave it to me.

42:30.000 --> 42:31.210
Even so, I still need an excuse

42:31.210 --> 42:31.650
to kick him out.

42:31.650 --> 42:33.000
Just say a new guest arrived

42:33.000 --> 42:34.070
and move him to a new room.

42:34.070 --> 42:34.710
Get him out of our room.

42:34.710 --> 42:35.820
What if I say that and he won't move?

42:35.820 --> 42:36.610
Give him some attitude!

42:36.610 --> 42:37.380
I don't have the nerve for that.

42:37.380 --> 42:38.820
My attitude wouldn't scare anyone.

42:38.820 --> 42:40.350
Are you going to do it or not?

42:41.300 --> 42:43.190
Could you give me just a moment to think?

42:43.190 --> 42:44.860
No need to think—just do it.

42:45.860 --> 42:47.030
You took it, so now you have to deliver.
